                    <p>Unlike traditional jewelers, The Diamond Shop is available 24 hours a day, seven days a week. We offer phone support, live chat, and e-mail with non-commissioned diamond and jewelry experts. Learn and shop the way you want, with no pressure, hassle-free 30-day return or exchange period.</p>
