                </div>

                <h3>Return the goods</h3>
                <div class="description">
                    <h4>What is your return policy?</h4>
                    <p>Our commitment to you doesn't end with delivery. Items can be returned or exchanged within 7 days of the date they were shipped, free of charge and no questions asked. To be eligible for a return, items must be in original condition when purchased and include all product documentation.</p>
                    <p>Items damaged by the user or damaged after the delivery person leaves will not be returned. Diamonds purchased as part of our The Diamond Shop Diamond Upgrade Program may not be returned for credit. All The Diamond Shop engraved rings can be returned for credit but engraving fees are non-refundable. Removal of The Diamond Shop engraving from any ring that is exchanged or resized is free of charge with no additional engraving fee. Special orders are final sale and are not eligible for return.</p>
