                <h3>Discounts</h3>
                <div class="description">
                    <h4>Are discounts available?</h4>
                    <p>Yes. You may stay informed on special offers and promotions by subscribing to the The Diamond Shop e-mail list. Sign up at the subscription status page.</p>
                </div>

                <h3>Shipping</h3>
                <div class="description">
                    <h4>How is my order packaged?</h4>
                    <p>We ship using secure, non-descript packaging material. Inside, you'll see The Diamond Shop's elegantly branded gift packaging - ideal for gifting or personal storage.</p>
                    <h4>Can I track my order?</h4>
                    <p>Yes. On the day of shipment, we'll email you shipping confirmation that includes order-tracking information. You'll be kept informed of the transportation process at every step. You may also access shipping information by viewing your Order Status page.</p>
                </div>

