                    <p>Currently we can only pay through PayPal, and we do not accept cash payments. After we confirm your payment, we will prepare the goods and send them to you.</p>
                    <h4>Can I get a refund when I cancel my order?</h4>
                    <p>You can only cancel an order if the order is in "Order Placed" status.</p>
                </div>

                <h3>Warranty</h3>
                <div class="description">
                    <h4>Do you offer a warranty on the jewelry I purchase from The Diamond Shop?</h4>
                    <p>Yes. In staying true to our high standards of jewelry quality and customer satisfaction, we offer a Warranty to protect against manufacturer defects in craftsmanship. The warranty does not include normal wear and tear or damages incurred due to trauma, negligence, lack of regular maintenance, loss, or theft.</p>
                    <h4>How can I safeguard my purchase against damage, theft, or a loss?</h4>
